name: Harsh Barge & Other Stories Part 2
description: Part 2 of my ongoing memoir series. 5 new chapters, 32 pages, black and white text, and some photos.

name: Allergy Season #1
description: This is my first seasonal submission magazine, containing art, writing, and photography from myself and over 20 different contributors from all over. 52 black and white pages, memoirs of a "wicked pissah," interview with a local metal band, photo editorial by a KC skate photographer, secret video link, and much more. Contains some nudity, so I guess that means only 18+ can order. Run of 100, numbered and stapled.

name: Life Hammers / Down On You
description: Split poetry zine featuring two sides of my personality: "depressing" and "not depressing." The first side "Life Hammers" contains 16 unreleased poems, and the second side  "Down On You" (in which the zine must be flipped over to continue reading) contains 12 unreleased poems, plus a poem which was just published in a South Dakota literary journal, and one drawing. All of these have been written since May 2012 except for two old journal poems. Run of 100, numbered and stapled. Comes in various colored covers.

name: Harsh Barge
description:
This is a photo zine of over 80 film photographs taken over the summer of 2012, while traveling with my friend across SE Asia by motorbike, venturing through Vietnam, Cambodia, Thailand, India, and Nepal. No hotels, no bullshit, no fucks given. This is what "barging" looks like.

48 pages, Stapled, Numbered.
